1
00:01:29,530 --> 00:01:32,979
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,550 --> 00:01:36,110
[Episode 1]

3
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,680
Master.

4
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,730
[One month earlier...]

5
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,500
You're the only one who can't keep up.

6
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,310
I went to great lengths

7
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,860
to hide among these death row prisoners,

8
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:59,920
just to enter Lingya Tower

9
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,760
and find the antidote for my mother.

10
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,930
Master said Lingya Tower
is extremely well hidden.

11
00:03:05,930 --> 00:03:07,720
Lingya Tower has 8 levels,

12
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,590
each guarded by a voice-keeper

13
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,450
who leads a group of mute servants.

14
00:03:11,450 --> 00:03:13,600
The voice-keepers organize death matches,

15
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,520
forcing female prisoners
to fight one another to the death

16
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,920
for the entertainment of wealthy elites.

17
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:19,240
They treat human lives as worthless

18
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,840
and have no shred of conscience left.

19
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,079
For my mother,

20
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:26,020
I must enter this living hell
no matter what.

21
00:03:36,070 --> 00:03:36,990
Food is here.

22
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,390
How are we supposed to eat this?

23
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:52,500
It's gone bad.

24
00:04:01,850 --> 00:04:02,910
What do you mean?

25
00:04:04,350 --> 00:04:05,410
Say something!

26
00:04:05,450 --> 00:04:07,240
He's a mute servant. He can't speak.

27
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,720
He means

28
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:09,830
that by the time it's our turn,

29
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:11,080
this is all that'll be left for us.

30
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,130
What do you mean this is all that's left

31
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:13,520
by the time it's our turn?

32
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,320
Why is that?

33
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,520
Food

34
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,760
is distributed

35
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:17,899
from top to bottom here.

36
00:04:17,899 --> 00:04:19,220
Those at the top

37
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:20,740
always get to pick first.

38
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:34,820
Then how do we
get to the upper levels?

39
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:36,020
Each level of Lingya Tower

40
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:37,659
has a death match.

41
00:04:37,810 --> 00:04:39,340
The prisoners here fight,

42
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:41,070
wagering their lives on it.

43
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,580
If you win,

44
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,100
you move up a level.

45
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:46,080
If you reach the top,

46
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:48,140
you may win your freedom.

47
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,420
But if you lose,

48
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:54,100
you die.

49
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:56,400
Gambling with your life, huh?

50
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,580
If I want to join this death match,

51
00:04:59,020 --> 00:04:59,940
what should I do?

52
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:01,500
Then you'd better find a way

53
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:03,300
to meet the voice-keeper first.

54
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,780
How do I meet the voice-keeper then?

55
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:08,510
Unless you go looking for death,
it won't happen.

56
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:22,900
-Are you alright?
-Are you okay?

57
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:36,159
[Zhuang Wujiu, Level 1 Voice-keeper]

58
00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:41,840
In Lingya Tower,

59
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:43,370
suicide is the gravest taboo.

60
00:05:43,370 --> 00:05:44,970
Hasn't anyone told you that?

61
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,330
Speak.

62
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:48,460
What are you plotting?

63
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:52,300
I want to take part in the death match.

64
00:05:53,810 --> 00:05:55,090
It's been a long time

65
00:05:55,110 --> 00:05:57,040
since I saw someone so eager to die.

66
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,420
If you're looking for death,

67
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:06,100
I'll grant your wish.

68
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:12,620
Go.

69
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,940
[Death Match]

70
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:14,220
Report to the Tower Master.

71
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:17,380
A death match will be held
on the lowest level.

72
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,280
Don't take it.

73
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:30,350
Whoever takes it

74
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:31,980
has to enter the death match.

75
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,730
-A death match?
-A death match?

76
00:06:45,650 --> 00:06:47,450
If we're going to starve anyway,

77
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:49,850
we might as well fight for our lives.

78
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:51,990
-Yeah.
-Right.

79
00:06:51,990 --> 00:06:53,100
We might as well take our chances.

80
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:54,010
Yes. Better to risk our lives

81
00:06:54,010 --> 00:06:55,260
than starve to death.

82
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,300
Don't eat it.

83
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,980
Don't eat it.

84
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:16,020
Dear honored guests,

85
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:18,350
an additional match will
be held on the lowest level tonight.

86
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,340
I wonder

87
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:20,760
if you'd be interested.

88
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:22,460
What kind of match is it this time?

89
00:07:22,460 --> 00:07:23,740
Yes, how does it work?

90
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:26,000
How many female prisoners have arrived?

91
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:29,520
[Level 1: Eight-Trigrams Death Match]

92
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:44,260
Welcome, everyone,
to the Eight-Trigrams Death Match.

93
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,330
You have 10 drumbeats.

94
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:48,060
Only those who find the Gate of Life

95
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:50,480
[Qian] [Kun] [Zhen] [Xun]
[Kan] [Li] [Gen] [Dui]

96
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,659
may leave

97
00:07:49,659 --> 00:07:50,730
and advance to the next level.

98
00:07:50,730 --> 00:07:52,170
Let the death match

99
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,280
begin.

100
00:08:14,050 --> 00:08:15,580
You nearly scared me to death.

101
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:17,320
I thought you were
one of the mute servants.

102
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,350
Did you find…

103
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:57,250
Yanzhi.

104
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:03,780
It's me.

105
00:09:07,690 --> 00:09:09,490
I saw so many people die

106
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,240
on my way here.

107
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:14,540
This

108
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,420
drumbeat is deafening.

109
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:17,970
It's terrifying.

110
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:19,390
That's the 2nd drumbeat.

111
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:20,380
If we don't find the exit

112
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:21,420
before the 10th drumbeat,

113
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:22,480
we'll all die here.

114
00:09:23,170 --> 00:09:23,890
Huh?

115
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:27,100
Yanzhi.

116
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:28,730
Yanzhi.

117
00:09:29,050 --> 00:09:30,350
I don't want to die.

118
00:09:44,350 --> 00:09:45,150
This way.

119
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,380
An exit?

120
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,850
This isn't the real exit.

121
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:05,030
It's not real?

122
00:11:30,570 --> 00:11:31,250
Man,

123
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,650
how many drumbeats have there been?

124
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:34,170
If I remember correctly,

125
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:36,020
it should be the 6th drumbeat.

126
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:37,330
We're running out of time.

127
00:11:37,330 --> 00:11:39,190
We need to find the real exit fast.

128
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:40,310
Alright.

129
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:41,610
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

130
00:11:46,810 --> 00:11:47,810
How was it?

131
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,850
Dear honored guests,

132
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,100
are you satisfied with your picks?

133
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:52,030
I bet on 5 people,

134
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:52,870
and 4 of them died.

135
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:53,740
Damn, that's bad luck.

136
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:55,000
Play a few more rounds,

137
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,950
and you'll get the hang of it.

138
00:12:21,170 --> 00:12:22,370
Hurry.

139
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,150
That's the 7th drumbeat already.

140
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:34,900
Three more,

141
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,440
and we're done for, aren't we?

142
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:39,840
With so many doors, when are we
supposed to find the right one?

143
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,140
The note.

144
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:53,510
[Qian] [Kun] [Zhen] [Xun]
[Kan] [Li] [Gen] [Dui]

145
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,960
This map shows eight doors in total.

146
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:57,270
We've already checked 6 of them.

147
00:12:57,400 --> 00:13:02,480
[Qian] [Kun] [Zhen] [Xun]
[Kan] [Li] [Gen] [Dui]

148
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:58,750
My guess is

149
00:12:58,770 --> 00:13:00,020
that the Gate of Life lies

150
00:13:00,020 --> 00:13:02,340
in either the Qian or Dui direction.

151
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:03,740
We're running out of time—

152
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:04,860
we have to split up

153
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:06,520
if we want a chance to survive.

154
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,310
Alright,

155
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,590
you take this door.

156
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:12,340
I'll go over there.

157
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,540
Hey, take this,

158
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:15,540
and take care of yourself.

